</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <strong><a href="http://www.gnome-look.org/index.php?xsortmode=down&amp;xcontentmode=101" class="urlextern" title="http://www.gnome-look.org/index.php?xsortmode=down&amp;xcontentmode=101"  rel="nofollow">Metacity</a></strong>, <a href="http://browse.deviantart.com/customization/skins/linuxutil/gnome/gtk2/#catpath=customization/skins/linuxutil/gnome/metacity&amp;order=9" class="urlextern" title="http://browse.deviantart.com/customization/skins/linuxutil/gnome/gtk2/#catpath=customization/skins/linuxutil/gnome/metacity&amp;order=9"  rel="nofollow">DeviantArt</a> : permet de modifier la bordure des fenêtres.</div>
